Bellrunner
========================

sox, mp3splt, ffmpeg

Install ffmepg
--------------
        sudo apt-get install ffmpeg

Intall mp3splt
--------------
        http://mp3splt.sourceforge.net/mp3splt_page/debian_downloads.php?version=Precise&ubuntu=true
        or sudo apt-get install mp3splt


Install sox
-----------
        sudo apt-get install sox libsox-fmt-all libsox-fmt-mp3 libsox-fmt-ffmpeg